Description
-----------

Defines a preview image for use in the level editor.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    qer_editorimage [map]

Parameters
----------

-   [map] - the relative path and file name from base to the specified preview image.

Notes
-----

The image specified will be used in the texture and media inspectors as well as the 3D preview window when realtime rendering is not enabled.

